---
title: Bonfire Night Honey-Mustard Pulled Pork Dog with Wedges and Apple & Baby Leaf Salad
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, this tasty Bonfire Night Honey-Mustard Pulled Pork Dog is perfect for a casual sharing-style dinner. It's great for cosying up with for Bonfire Night this November 5th!
